name: Moonlight Fiziks
bio: David Morales better known as Moonlight Fiziks. Is an upcoming electronic artist based out of Visalia, CA. He has currently released music with labels such as: Box of Cats (AUS), Space Yacht (LA), Artichokes Are Yellow, Red Paradise Records (Brazil), Fresh Baked (LA) , Rock Bottom Records (LA) , Brash Beats (UK), & UFO Records (Brazil). He has shared the stage with such acts as A-Trak, DJ Diesel, Madeon, Omnom, Lubelski, Sacha Robotti, Golf Clap, Ms. Worthy & more. A couple of his latest accomplishments was being featured on the Dirtybird Twitch channel for their Online festival and having his “Get Weird” EP hit #1 on the Top Bass House Releases Chart on Beatport during its initial release.
